headline: DoorDash and Coco Robotics Expand Partnership to Miami, Broadening Autonomous Delivery Across Grocery and Retail
summary: Coco Robotics, a leading autonomous delivery company, and DoorDash, a leading local commerce platform, today announced an expansion of their partnership to scale autonomous deliveries across Los Angeles, Chicago, and, for the first time, Miami.
